-- Manchester United to Meet West Ham in English League Cup Quarterfinals
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2010-10-30T12:52:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-30/manchester-united-to-meet-west-ham-in-english-league-cup-quarterfinals.html
Defending champion Manchester United
will visit West Ham in the quarterfinals of English soccer’s
League Cup.  Arsenal hosts Wigan and Birmingham faces local rival Aston
Villa in other all-Premier League matchups determined by today’s
draw. Ipswich, the only team from outside the top flight still
in the competition, meets West Bromwich Albion in the final
game.  The quarterfinal matches will be played the week beginning
Nov. 29.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  